DESCRIPTION:Reach out to your dealer to confirm timing and availability\n\n
 Small group call on Wednesday\, April 29th.\nIssuer: FULTON FINL CORP (FUL
 T)\n\nDeal context:\nFulton Financial Corporation is conducting fixed inco
 me investor calls on April 29-30\, organized by Piper Sandler and J.P. Mor
 gan\, ahead of a potential subordinated notes offering. Subject to market 
